# Salin file ini menjadi .env dan isi nilainya

# Google Sheets API Key
# Dapatkan dari: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 1. Buat project baru
# 2. Aktifkan "Google Sheets API" di Library
# 3. Buat API Key di Credentials
# 4. (Opsional) Batasi API key ke Google Sheets API saja
PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SHEETS_API_KEY=AIzaSyAA9BJvIMaRxTT-gqnbdxm8TIeTqNv4neA

# =============================================================
# CARA SETUP GOOGLE SHEETS:
# =============================================================
# 1. Buka Google Sheets Anda
# 2. File > Share > Anyone with the link > Viewer
# 3. Copy Spreadsheet ID dari URL:
#    https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/[SPREADSHEET_ID]/edit
# 4. Paste ID di src/lib/googleSheets.ts pada SHEETS_CONFIG.SPREADSHEET_ID
# =============================================================
